During the rise of new continents<lb/>
and islands assumed to have taken place<lb/>
it necessarily follows that the waters<lb/>
must have flowed in upon the lands already<lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">existing.</hi>.-<lb/>
