            <lb/>
the primeval <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">lands</hi> were broken down<lb/>
and covered by the Ocean which rushed<lb/>
into the abyss that they had overspread<lb/>
and that the present Islands and<lb/>
continents which before existed in the<lb/>
water were inconsequence uncovered<lb/>
so that the places of the land and<lb/>
sea were altogether changed.-<lb/>
