            <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">opposites</del>
            <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">affinities</add> in consequence of which certain substances<lb/>
before dissolved were <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
