chrystalized form but rather in a state of<lb/>
Mechanical division and from their mixture<lb/>
with the substances of primitive <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">formation</hi>
