                facs="#i49"/>
            <lb/>
depositions had rendered free so as to make<lb/>
them to be thrown down <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">in regular strata</hi>
